</Rewrite>

<New PAsource="" >Scrap
</New>

<New PAsource="" >Yesterday, singer Liam still appeared to be reeling from Bonehead's announcement.
</New>

<New PAsource="" >He refused to comment when he appeared briefly alongside wife Patsy Kensit outside their house in Primrose Hill, north London.
</New>

<New PAsource="" >But there's no doubt that Bonehead's decision has hit him hard.
</New>

<New PAsource="" >"He was Liam's best mate in the band. They used to have the odd scrap, but they were really close," says a band source.
</New>

